      "span_text": "Welcomed for their potential to enhance connectivity between the school and the workplace (Wesselink et al., 2009) , the approaches based on competences re-opened theoretical debates and empirical investigation on the relationships between knowledge and its application, and more broadly between theory and praxis  .",
